[Unit]
Description=Calendar App Backend (Spring Boot)
After=network.target mysql.service

[Service]
User=ubuntu
WorkingDirectory=/home/ubuntu/app/calendar-app/backend
ExecStart=/usr/bin/java -jar target/calendar-app-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar
Restart=always
RestartSec=5

Environment=SPRING_PROFILES_ACTIVE=prod
Environment=DB_USER=your_db_user
Environment=DB_PASSWORD=your_db_password
Environment=DB_HOST=localhost
Environment=DB_NAME=calendar

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target

MySQL database and user creation is done manually.
Environment variables are configured in the backend systemd service.
